Modifications
================================================================================

This project adapts codex-plugin-cc for Grok Build instead of Codex. Notable
changes include:

  - Replacement of Codex app-server integration with Grok ACP (grok agent stdio)
  - New modules: acp-client.mjs, grok.mjs, acp-broker.mjs
  - Grok-specific companion CLI (grok-companion.mjs), skills, and plugin metadata
  - Prompt-based code review (Grok has no native review/start RPC)
  - Session resume via ACP session/load instead of Codex thread/resume

Files with substantial derivation from codex-plugin-cc include:

  plugins/grok/scripts/grok-companion.mjs
  plugins/grok/scripts/acp-broker.mjs
